
  SKID ROW GIVE YOU THE DOX TO ---===== GODFATHER =====--- TYPED BY SCOOTER
  -------===============------          --=====--          ----========----

SCENARIO 
---------
LEVEL 1:

THE SETTING IS NEW YORK IN THE 1940`S. YOU FIND YOURSELF WALKING IN THE BACK
STREETS OF A RUN DOWN NEIGHBOURHOOD,IN THE EARLY EVENING.
YOU ENTER A LOCAL BAR WHICH AT FIRST APPEARS TO BE DESERTED,TAKE CARE...IN 
YOUR LINE OF BUSINESS THINGS ARE `NOT OFTEN AS THEY SEEM`.
FURTHER ALONG THE STREET YOU FIND A BARBERS SHOP.UPON ENTERING THERE IS A
DEADLY SILENCE. ANTICIPATING A POSSIBLE ATTACK YOU BRACE YOURSELF FOR WHAT 
LIES AHEAD.

LEVEL 2:

THE 1950`S STREETS OF LAS VEGAS IS THE NEXT SETTING,BRIGHTLY LIT AND FULL
OF ACTIVITY.PEDESTRIANS GO ABOUT THE EVENINGS BUSINESS HEADING FOR THE CAFE`S
BARS,AND CASINOS.
AS YOU HEAD DOWN THE STREET,YOU WITNESS AN EXPLOSION AT A NEARBY FAMILY RUN
CASINO. YOU CONSIDER FOUL PLAY WHEN YOU SEE THE BOMBERS FLEEING THE SCENE.
YOUR NEXT OBJECTIVE IS TO ENTER THE COLESSIUM CASINO AND GAIN REVENGE FOR THE
BOMBING,TAKING OUT OPPOSING FAMILY HOODS. GO CAREFULLY YOU DONT WANT TO HARM
INNOCENT BYSTANDERS.

LEVEL 3:

HAVANA, CUBA..JUST BEFORE THE REVOLUTION. AS YOU WALK THROUGH THE POOR PART 
OF TOWN,YOU CAN SEE THE SWANKY HOTELS CONTROLLED BY THE MOB IN THE BACKGROUND
AMIDST THE REMAINS OF A SHANTY TOWN STANDS THE OPULENT MANSION OF HYMAN ROTH.
YOU NEED TO ENTER THIS MANSION BUT BEWARE - THE GROUNDS ARE CRAWLING WITH
HENCHMEN WHO AIM TO STOP YOU DEAD IN YOUR TRACKS!.

LEVEL 4:

THE LUXURIOUS SURROUNDINGS OF AN EXCLUSIVE MARINA SOMEWHERE IN MIAMI DURING
THE 1970`S IS WHERE THE NEXT LEVEL TAKES PLACE.
THE MARINA IS FILLED WITH YAUGHTS MOORED TO THE JETTY. IN HOT PURSUIT OF THE
BADDIES YOU FIND YOUR OPPONENTS HUGE OCEAN GOING MOTOR CRUISER,AND FIGHT YOUR
WAY ON BOARD.

LEVEL 5:

AFTER SURVIVING A NUMBER OF AMBUSHES,YOU ARRIVE AT THE GATES OF ONE OF THE
FAMILY HOMES.SET IN A SMALL TOWN IN AMERICA IT IS NOW THE 1980`S.
ALL THE HEADS OF THE FAMILIES ARE PRESENT.HIS IS THE FINAL CONFRONATION,YOU
MUST DEFEND THE ASSEMBLED BY DESTROYING THE HELICOPTER AND ITS CREW OF
ASSASSINS. YOUR SUCCESS WILL CEMENT A NEAR PEACE BETWEEN RIVAL FAMILIES,
AND THE PLAYER WILL RECIEVE REWARD FROM HIS PWN DON.
FAILURE TO DO THIS MEANS THE BLOODY WAR WILL CONTINUE.

CONTROL SUMMARY(STREET SECTIONS)
---------------

              
                      DIRECTION `WITHOUT` FIRE
                      ------------------------

JOYSTICK CENTRE AND UP
----------------------
ONTO LADDER/INTO DOOR/FROM GUTTER IN CHOSEN DIRECTION.

JOYSTICK UP AND LEFT/RIGHT
--------------------------
MOVE FROM GUTTER TO PATH IN CHOSEN DIRECTION.

JOYSTICK MIDDLE AND LEFT/RIGHT
------------------------------
(LONG PRESS)  WALK IN CHOSEN DIRECTION.
(SHORT PRESS) DODGE.(SHORT QUICK STEPS) IN CHOSEN DIRECTION - FOR USE IN
DODGING BULLETS ect... 

JOYSTICK PULLED DOWN AND LEFT/RIGHT
-----------------------------------
MOVE FROM PATH TO GUTTER IN CHOSEN DIRECTION.

JOYSTICK PULLED DOWN AND CENTRE
-------------------------------
CROUCH -(IF JOYSTICK CENTRELEFT/RIGHT) THEN PRESSED FIRE IN CHOSEN DIRECTION
WHILST CROUCHED.

                      DIRECTION `WITH` FIRE
                      ---------------------

JOYSTICK PULLED DOWN AND CENTRE
-------------------------------
CROUCH AND FIRE.

NO DIRECTION
------------
DRAW GUN IN CURRENT DIRECTION FACING(EXCEPT WHEN ON LADDER).

OTHERS
------
SHOOT IN THAT DIRECTION.

CURSOR MOVEMENTS..NORMAL..ARROW UP GO UP..DOWN GO DOWN..LEFT GO LEFT ect...

HARD DISK INSTALLATION
----------------------
TO INSTALL GODFATHER ON YOUR HARDDISK SIMPLY INSERT DISK 1 INTO YOUR INTERNAL
DRIVE AND AT THE PROMPT ENTER `INSTAll` AND PRESS ENTER THEN FOLLOW THE
INSTRUCTIONS AS THEY APPEAR ON THE SCREEN.ONCE `GODFATHER` HAS BEEN INSTALLED
YOU MAY RUN THE GAME BY TYPING AT THE ROOT DIRECTORY PROMPT.
`CD/GOD` AND PRESS ENTER..`GOD`AND PRESS ENTER FOLLOW THE SCREEN INSTRUCTIONS.

                    AND THAT IT...SCOOTER -23/12/91-
